%N A394715 Decimal expansion of (1/zeta(4)) * Sum_{p prime} 1/(p^4-1).
%C A394715 The asymptotic probability that the greatest common square divisor of two positive integers selected independently at random is a prime power (not including 1, i.e., A056798 \ {1}).
%F A394715 Equals (1/zeta(4)) * Sum_{k>=1} P(4*k), where P is the prime zeta function.
%e A394715 0.0751317800794047337553663344221169780971903740559052...
%o A394715 (PARI) sumeulerrat(1/(p^4-1)) / zeta(4)
